220
00:12:59,380 --> 00:13:01,229
Online social platforms

221
00:13:01,339 --> 00:13:03,630
have become places where love happens.

222
00:13:04,260 --> 00:13:07,379
However, this vast social market

223
00:13:07,380 --> 00:13:08,379
has also bred

224
00:13:08,380 --> 00:13:10,589
numerous romance scams.

225
00:13:12,459 --> 00:13:13,749
Pig-butchering scams

226
00:13:13,979 --> 00:13:15,738
occur when victims

227
00:13:15,739 --> 00:13:17,150
are seeking care.

228
00:13:17,459 --> 00:13:18,338
They provide us

229
00:13:18,339 --> 00:13:19,978
with high emotional support

230
00:13:19,979 --> 00:13:21,190
and companionship.

231
00:13:21,459 --> 00:13:22,670
And so,

232
00:13:22,979 --> 00:13:24,338
it's easier for them

233
00:13:24,339 --> 00:13:26,630
to control us emotionally.

234
00:13:26,739 --> 00:13:27,698
When victims

235
00:13:27,699 --> 00:13:28,738
raise doubts

236
00:13:28,739 --> 00:13:30,539
about investments

237
00:13:30,540 --> 00:13:31,858
or anything involving monetary matters,

238
00:13:31,859 --> 00:13:33,139
those scammers

239
00:13:33,140 --> 00:13:34,818
coerce or entice them

240
00:13:34,819 --> 00:13:36,698
into making impulsive decisions

241
00:13:36,699 --> 00:13:37,858
like investment.

242
00:13:37,859 --> 00:13:39,390
As a result,

243
00:13:39,540 --> 00:13:40,738
victims lose

244
00:13:40,739 --> 00:13:42,498
both love and money.

245
00:13:42,499 --> 00:13:44,379
So when you encounter
situations like this,

246
00:13:44,380 --> 00:13:46,030
you have to believe

247
00:13:46,140 --> 00:13:47,858
that those who truly care about you

248
00:13:47,859 --> 00:13:49,630
would encourage you to work hard
for your money.

249
00:13:50,020 --> 00:13:51,349
Only scammers

250
00:13:51,420 --> 00:13:53,630
coax you into making money overnight.

251
00:13:53,940 --> 00:13:55,910
We ourselves have experienced
pig-butchering scams.

252
