♪Midnight, a piercing chill♪

290
00:16:32,920 --> 00:16:36,590
♪Wakes you up from a shattered dream♪

291
00:16:38,920 --> 00:16:40,879
♪Heavy mist shrouds the truth♪

292
00:16:40,880 --> 00:16:42,879
♪A steadfast retaliation comes alive♪

293
00:16:42,880 --> 00:16:46,950
♪Oh, men, those smarty-pants♪

294
00:16:47,840 --> 00:16:50,279
♪The backfire of your overflowing charm♪

295
00:16:50,280 --> 00:16:54,070
♪Has no mercy♪

296
00:16:54,800 --> 00:16:57,639
♪May your life be barren♪

297
00:16:57,640 --> 00:16:59,919
♪May you tread on a thorny path alone♪

298
00:16:59,920 --> 00:17:01,399
♪May you vanish into thin air♪

299
00:17:01,400 --> 00:17:03,119
♪Lies will adorn your tombstone♪

300
00:17:03,120 --> 00:17:05,599
♪Release me from this hatred♪

301
00:17:05,600 --> 00:17:07,830
♪Free me from this excruciating cage♪

302
00:17:07,880 --> 00:17:09,399
♪Let me go to light♪

303
00:17:09,400 --> 00:17:11,959
♪Let's never meet again♪

304
00:17:11,960 --> 00:17:13,439
♪When I use your words♪

305
00:17:13,440 --> 00:17:14,399
♪And your ways♪

306
00:17:14,400 --> 00:17:16,799
♪You blame me for being cruel♪

307
00:17:16,800 --> 00:17:19,799
♪Life is ironic♪

308
00:17:19,800 --> 00:17:21,279
♪I want your end♪

309
00:17:21,280 --> 00:17:22,359
♪To be lonely♪

310
00:17:22,360 --> 00:17:25,230
♪With no one to hate♪

311
00:17:25,360 --> 00:17:29,070
♪You will live in endless nightmares♪

312
00:17:46,000 --> 00:17:48,870
♪Rise♪

313
00:17:51,520 --> 00:17:53,190
♪From the ashes♪
